# Build-specific ignore for docker/Dockerfile.zk-setup. Unlike the audit build,
# the ceremony NEEDS the full proofs/ tree (circuits, setup_circuits.sh,
# package*.json, vendor) AND the whole Cargo workspace (export_ark_zkey /
# generate_manifest are olympus-desktop bins). So keep almost everything; just
# drop the heavy/irrelevant: build outputs, deps, the multi-GB ptau (the script
# re-downloads it), and editor/VCS cruft.
.git
target
**/target
node_modules
**/node_modules
*.ptau
**/*.ptau
.claude
app/public-ui/dist
*.log
